/*+ NoMergeJoin(ci rt an1) NoMergeJoin(an1 ci rt t) NoMergeJoin(an1 ci rt t mc) NoMergeJoin(an1 ci mc rt t cn) NoMergeJoin(an1 ci cn mc rt t n1) */ select min(an1.name) AS costume_designer_pseudo,
min(t.title) AS movie_with_costumes
from role_type AS rt
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.role_id = rt.id AND rt.role = 'miscellaneous crew'
inner join aka_name AS an1
on an1.person_id = ci.person_id
inner join title AS t
on ci.movie_id = t.id
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id
inner join company_name AS cn
on mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code = '[nl]'
inner join name AS n1
on an1.person_id = n1.id AND n1.id = ci.person_id;
